  "detailed_description": "Sunset Shapes is a puzzle game where you connect broken pieces into a single object to cast a shadow. That shadow will reveal a shape of an object that makes part of a scene displayed in a mural.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/aa496260cb2be13e8440de6fd62aa97d.poster.avif?t=1599605433\" width=436 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/aa496260cb2be13e8440de6fd62aa97d.webm?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/aa496260cb2be13e8440de6fd62aa97d.mp4?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Travel alongside with a Daisy and a Maggot through several scenarios and discover to where they are headed to.<br><br>In each level, all pieces fall in the play ground.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/6145f4f2a4321493c34d8dbaad14a428.poster.avif?t=1599605433\" width=436 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/6145f4f2a4321493c34d8dbaad14a428.webm?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/6145f4f2a4321493c34d8dbaad14a428.mp4?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Then You must move and rotate them, so they fit inside the delimited zone. All levels have different pieces to connect.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/4bd97f8bcd5762f2bb49ebbeb76f464b.poster.avif?t=1599605433\" width=436 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/4bd97f8bcd5762f2bb49ebbeb76f464b.webm?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/4bd97f8bcd5762f2bb49ebbeb76f464b.mp4?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/812d1fd46166b09ad39baa7e81e68e88.poster.avif?t=1599605433\" width=436 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/812d1fd46166b09ad39baa7e81e68e88.webm?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/812d1fd46166b09ad39baa7e81e68e88.mp4?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/91b8d7189d1bdf0b24b2e26f2cc870db.poster.avif?t=1599605433\" width=436 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/91b8d7189d1bdf0b24b2e26f2cc870db.webm?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1300390/extras/91b8d7189d1bdf0b24b2e26f2cc870db.mp4?t=1599605433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Walk along the mural and play 50 hand-crafted levels while listening a relaxing piano music.",
